        "These are the backbone of Temecula's residential market — master-planned communities built primarily 2000–2015 with HOA management and consistent housing stock. Appliances here are Samsung, LG, KitchenAid, and Whirlpool from the mid-2010s, now in the prime failure window at 8–12 years. Samsung French-door refrigerators with ice maker issues, LG front-load washers with bearing wear, and Bosch dishwashers with hard water scale are the most common calls. Temecula water is hard — similar to the rest of Riverside County — and we descale as part of most dishwasher and ice maker calls here.",
